tomboy-ng (0.35-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  *  Release of new version
  * A better Search all notes and Find in Note capability.
  * A Ukrainian Translation.
  * UI tweaks including Ctrl-F toggling, Esc to close note.
  * A revised CLI, import, plain text, RTF and Markdown.
  * Ctrl-Z (ie Undo) will now revert an errant Date Stamp
  * A handful of minor bug fixes.
  * (Closes: #997942)
  * Please see github for further change details

